<section class="newsletter-cta">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-content">
      <h2>Non perderti un colpo</h2>
      <p>Ogni settimana ricevi un'analisi su bias cognitivi, errori finanziari e psicologia del denaro. Niente spam, solo roba utile.</p>
      
      <form class="newsletter-form" action="#" method="POST">
        <div class="form-group">
          <input 
            type="email" 
            name="email" 
            placeholder="La tua email" 
            required 
            aria-label="Indirizzo email"
          />
          <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">Iscriviti</button>
        </div>
        <p class="form-note">Gratis. Puoi cancellarti quando vuoi.</p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .newsletter-cta {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--secondary) 100%);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .cta-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .newsletter-form {
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .form-group {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .form-group input {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 0.875rem 1.25rem;
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-family: inherit;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .form-group input:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .form-group input::placeholder {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .btn-submit {
    padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--bg);
    border: none;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .btn-submit:hover {
    background: var(--accent-hover);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .form-note {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .newsletter-cta {
      padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .cta-content h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .form-group {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .btn-submit {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
